<script>
import { GrowBottomNavigation } from "bottom-navigation-vue";
import "bottom-navigation-vue/dist/style.css";

export default {
  components: { GrowBottomNavigation },
  data: () => ({
    selected: 1,
    options: [
      { id: 1, icon: "fa-solid fa-utensils", title: "Menu", color: "#5639af" },
      { id: 2, icon: "fa-solid fa-calendar", title: "Plan", color: "#ac4793" },
      {
        id: 3,
        icon: "fa-solid fa-cart-shopping",
        title: "List",
        color: "#e2a93a",
      },
    ],
  }),
};
</script>

<template>
  <GrowBottomNavigation :options="options" v-model="selected" />
</template>
